cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.SD 

The paper deals with image processing and specifically with removing camera shake from images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. The paper also involves Fourier analysis, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation of the algorithm on camera phones, which could fall under the systems and control (cs.SD) category.
